Package: Homework6
Title: Sparse Numeric Vector Class and Operations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jana", "Kassem", email = "jana.kassem@utexas.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides an S4 class for sparse numeric vectors along with arithmetic 
    operations, norms, and standardization implemented without converting 
    to dense format. Includes documentation, unit tests, and a pkgdown 
    website for function documentation.
